  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Kingdom in Peril</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For generations, the people of Mercia have suffered under the rule of the dark sorceress Etheldred. Every seven years, her armies sweep across the land to abduct the innocent, never to be seen again. Now, the call for heroes has gone out one last time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/38d1f7fffc63ab935b30caeceac39895.poster.avif?t=1761748194\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/38d1f7fffc63ab935b30caeceac39895.webm?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/38d1f7fffc63ab935b30caeceac39895.mp4?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arcade Action Returns</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle Axe is a top-down hack and slash adventure inspired by the golden age of arcade games. Featuring detailed pixel art by industry veteran Henk Nieborg and a rousing soundtrack from Manami Matsumae, this is a true tribute to classic gaming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/7f6dffb4940914f189b3a4012cda4383.poster.avif?t=1761748194\" width=612 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/7f6dffb4940914f189b3a4012cda4383.webm?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/7f6dffb4940914f189b3a4012cda4383.mp4?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Champion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from three fearless heroes, each with unique abilities and weapons.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fae the swift elven warrior fights with twin blades and throwing daggers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Iolo the bearded druid lashes enemies and casts deadly fireballs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rooney the marauder crushes foes up close or fires cannonballs from afar</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through hordes of monsters and take down powerful bosses to reach Etheldred's stronghold in the North.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/af7cea95c8f35946e135ffbdc6efceac.avif?t=1761748194\" width=612 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Classic Combat with a Modern Touch</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack in eight directions with a mix of melee strikes and ranged projectiles. Collect gold, find powerful scrolls and potions, and visit the mysterious merchant Ælfwyn to upgrade your gear between battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/3b1cff24934fd861fbc3eec91d48e95e.poster.avif?t=1761748194\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/3b1cff24934fd861fbc3eec91d48e95e.webm?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/3b1cff24934fd861fbc3eec91d48e95e.mp4?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is where you come in, brave champion…help us save the kingdom of Mercia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/bc030080df7a1c2da01cc3b4c0f8787e.poster.avif?t=1761748194\" width=612 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/bc030080df7a1c2da01cc3b4c0f8787e.webm?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/bc030080df7a1c2da01cc3b4c0f8787e.mp4?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced hack and slash gameplay with a retro arcade feel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-player and local co-op for heroic team play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorgeous handcrafted pixel art across four unique regions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soundtrack by legendary composer Manami Matsumae</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging boss fights and satisfying enemy waves</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Kingdom in Peril</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For generations, the people of Mercia have suffered under the rule of the dark sorceress Etheldred. Every seven years, her armies sweep across the land to abduct the innocent, never to be seen again. Now, the call for heroes has gone out one last time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/38d1f7fffc63ab935b30caeceac39895.poster.avif?t=1761748194\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/38d1f7fffc63ab935b30caeceac39895.webm?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/38d1f7fffc63ab935b30caeceac39895.mp4?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arcade Action Returns</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle Axe is a top-down hack and slash adventure inspired by the golden age of arcade games. Featuring detailed pixel art by industry veteran Henk Nieborg and a rousing soundtrack from Manami Matsumae, this is a true tribute to classic gaming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/7f6dffb4940914f189b3a4012cda4383.poster.avif?t=1761748194\" width=612 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1167300/extras/7f6dffb4940914f189b3a4012cda4383.webm?t=1761748194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.ak